title: tearing our old code and putting in new
message:
tearing our old code and putting in new

Basic flow is still the same but now the objects have a more semanticly
correct names

* ApplicationList is the ArrayAdapter which holds all the Applications
* Application is the actual list item's View and has a list of Versions
* VersionList is another ArrayAdapter that has the Versions for that
  Application which holds it
* Version lastly is the list item view of each application version

cleaned out the older AsyncTasks for slightly cleaner new ones which
creates Applications and Versions and addes them to the their Adapters
